---
title: Carb Smart BBQ-Rubbed Pork Chops with Salad and Roasted Broccoli
description: Is there anything better than seasoned pork slathered in sweet and tangy BBQ sauce? We think not. It's the main feature of this tasty carb-smart meal, with broccoli and salad coming alongside to create a perfect dinner plate.

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
